{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/creative/invitation/","webpackCompilationHash":"","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"6048bde1-d002-5c59-914c-b7b3409ad3fd","excerpt":"…","html":"<p>有一个朋友要结婚了，想找我做一个婚礼邀请函。他是一个程序员，想要自己的婚礼邀请函既能体现自己的职业特点，也要与众不同。</p>\n<p>我想了一下，说到程序员一般人会想到什么呢？那一定是一个人在屏幕前敲代码，所以我可以从敲代码入手。不如让这个邀请函一进来就是一个代码编辑器，而代码编辑器中有一段代码正在编辑，就好像打开邀请函的人看见了我的朋友在写代码。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/start-6be2b96544679d828850413dc1746280.gif\"></p>\n<p>当代码写完之后，就弹出一个正式的邀请函吧。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/2b872/invite.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"invite\"\n        title=\"invite\"\n        src=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/e2288/invite.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/264cc/invite.jpg 160w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/f562b/invite.jpg 320w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/e2288/invite.jpg 640w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/b3ee8/invite.jpg 960w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/6c315/invite.jpg 1280w,\n/static/b380b1e40cd98573507e0ceb814996fd/2b872/invite.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>点击邀请函，它就会自动展开，展示出里面的内页。这里，会有我朋友的结婚照，以及相关的婚礼信息。你可能会注意到，在内页中还有一个输入框可以写下祝福语。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/2b872/wish.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"wish\"\n        title=\"wish\"\n        src=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/e2288/wish.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/264cc/wish.jpg 160w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/f562b/wish.jpg 320w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/e2288/wish.jpg 640w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/b3ee8/wish.jpg 960w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/6c315/wish.jpg 1280w,\n/static/5d63d18010c08a5be19b6fa66439c4cd/2b872/wish.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>写下祝福语，按回车就可以发送出去啦。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 640px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/2b872/barrage.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 80.546875%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"barrage\"\n        title=\"barrage\"\n        src=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/e2288/barrage.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/264cc/barrage.jpg 160w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/f562b/barrage.jpg 320w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/e2288/barrage.jpg 640w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/b3ee8/barrage.jpg 960w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/6c315/barrage.jpg 1280w,\n/static/5d33565925314fdb529ca349a540bdfc/2b872/barrage.jpg 2560w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 640px) 100vw, 640px\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>这就是我给朋友做的婚礼邀请函。</p>","frontmatter":{"title":"程序猿的邀请函","date":"2015/11/28","description":"用代码定制一个邀请函。","color":"#151633","cover":"invitation.jpg","demo":"demos/invitation.png","demoText":null}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/creative/invitation/","previous":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/brush-timeline/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"帮你刷朋友圈的小工具"}},"next":{"fields":{"slug":"/creative/sketch-jike-plugin/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Sketch 刷即刻插件"}}}}}